Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###
# Hard delete (borrado físico) un cliente
DELETE http://localhost:5000/clients/{{client_id}}/hard
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###
# Listar todos los clientes archivados (soft-deleted)
